- He don't got it.

535
00:21:36.587 --> 00:21:39.048
Barry. what did you do?

536
00:21:39.089 --> 00:21:41.175
We're trying
to fix the universe!

537
00:21:41.258 --> 00:21:42.384
(CHUCKLES)
I don't want it fixed!

538
00:21:42.468 --> 00:21:43.969
I wike it the way it is.

539
00:21:44.053 --> 00:21:45.095
We don't.

540
00:21:45.179 --> 00:21:47.264
- ♪ (DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
- (BARRY KRIPKE GROANS)

541
00:21:47.932 --> 00:21:49.475
Raj. talk to me. buddy!

542
00:21:49.558 --> 00:21:51.727
(BREATHES HEAVILY)
I'm okay. I'm okay.

543
00:21:52.937 --> 00:21:54.396
(GROANS) Maybe not.

544
00:21:54.480 --> 00:21:57.399
- STUART: (GASPS. EXCLAIMS) Raj?
- (GROANS WEAKLY)

545
00:21:58.108 --> 00:21:59.068
Ow!

546
00:21:59.109 --> 00:22:00.402
- (BERT GRUNTS)
- (GROANS)

547
00:22:00.444 --> 00:22:02.571
W... What do we do?
How do we fix the machine?

548
00:22:02.655 --> 00:22:04.240
- ♪ (SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
- Oh. look!

549
00:22:04.323 --> 00:22:08.869
It's my grandmother. Ambulu.
beckoning me to join her!

550
00:22:08.953 --> 00:22:10.412
Ca-- Can... Can she
wait a minute?

551
00:22:10.454 --> 00:22:12.248
- (GROANS)
- Apparently not.

552
00:22:12.289 --> 00:22:13.249
- (WHIMPERS)
- DENISE: Okay.

553
00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:15.751
- (BERT GRUNTS)
- Ow! Ow!

554
00:22:15.793 --> 00:22:17.336
STUART: What do we do?
What do we do?

555
00:22:17.419 --> 00:22:18.671
Uh... (STAMMERS)
Set the impedance

556
00:22:18.754 --> 00:22:20.881
- to point seven.
- (STAMMERS) The what?

557
00:22:20.965 --> 00:22:22.383
- DENISE: Yeah. right here.
- STUART: Ah. ah!

558
00:22:23.050 --> 00:22:24.593
(CHOKES)

559
00:22:24.635 --> 00:22:26.804
(WHIMPERS) Okay. uh...

560
00:22:26.887 --> 00:22:29.974
- Uh. disengage the attenuator.
- Okay. (STAMMERS) Mm...

561
00:22:30.766 --> 00:22:32.852
(STRAINS) Ow.

562
00:22:32.935 --> 00:22:34.603
- (DEVICE DINGS)
- Okay.

563
00:22:34.687 --> 00:22:35.813
Turn the main release.

564
00:22:35.896 --> 00:22:36.981
(STUART WHIMPERS)

565
00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:40.150
- (GRUNTS)
- (BERT GROANS)

566
00:22:40.234 --> 00:22:41.235
Uh...

567
00:22:41.861 --> 00:22:43.988
(DEVICE CHIMES. ROARS)

568
00:22:44.071 --> 00:22:45.990
- Done!
- But first...

569
00:22:46.073 --> 00:22:48.242
"But first"?
What do you mean "but first"?

570
00:22:48.325 --> 00:22:50.536
- Oh. oh!
- (GASPS)

571
00:22:51.161 --> 00:22:53.914
(DEVICE RUMBLES. ROARS)

572
00:22:53.998 --> 00:22:55.749
Uh... This is upsetting!

573
00:22:56.542 --> 00:22:57.918
(WHIMPERS)

574
00:22:58.002 --> 00:22:59.211
- Should it be glowing?
- (DEVICE BEEPS)

575
00:22:59.295 --> 00:23:00.421
(DRONING WARBLE)

576
00:23:00.504 --> 00:23:02.047
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

577
00:23:06.927 --> 00:23:10.639
- (WHOOSHING WARBLE)
- (ECHOING SCREAMS)

578
00:23:10.723 --> 00:23:13.100
♪ (INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

579
00:23:13.183 --> 00:23:15.895
♪ (MUSIC TURNS EERIE) ♪

580
00:23:16.854 --> 00:23:17.980
Bert. stop.

581
00:23:18.063 --> 00:23:19.315
♪ (MUSIC STOPS) ♪

582
00:23:19.398 --> 00:23:21.191
