585
00:23:24.945 --> 00:23:26.155
No apocalypse.

586
00:23:26.238 --> 00:23:28.365
- (EXCITED CHATTER)
- ♪ (CHEERFUL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

587
00:23:28.449 --> 00:23:30.868
