- (BIRDS CHIRPING)

589
00:23:35.164 --> 00:23:36.624
Look how beautiful.

590
00:23:37.708 --> 00:23:40.377
Wats. my weign has ended.

591
00:23:41.795 --> 00:23:44.340
Hey. your bruises are gone.

592
00:23:44.423 --> 00:23:46.008
Oh. yeah.

593
00:23:46.091 --> 00:23:49.219
You wook good.
I mean... for you.

594
00:23:50.387 --> 00:23:52.640
- Where's Denise?
- I don't know.

595
00:23:54.183 --> 00:23:55.726
I can't lose her again.

596
00:23:55.809 --> 00:24:00.230
Don't worry. she's out there.
and we'll find her.

597
00:24:02.024 --> 00:24:04.068
